title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight -  Airbus H125 helicopter - version 1.0
description:
In this video we will look at the Airbus H125 helicopter which has been released today. The helicopter is still under development but a quick test flight showed already that it can be used although some functionality currently is missing. After we reviewed the exterior we will have a look at the cockpit and will try to see if we can uncover where all those buttons are for ;-)

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/25212/airbus-h125-helicopter-project
